{"tid":2097911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美雙航母南海軍演 「與華戰艦互望」","createTime":"2020-07-07T06:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T07:11:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dba90ebce201818694d7f8924f7cea05964f9693","tid":2097911,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200707/NPPF7Z64TR3ILJXFQWQICSG3OQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200707%2FNPPF7Z64TR3ILJXFQWQICSG3OQ%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=a3b2edf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200707%2FNPPF7Z64TR3ILJXFQWQICSG3OQ%2F&h=ccd502f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200707/NPPF7Z64TR3ILJXFQWQICSG3OQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美雙航母南海軍演 「與華戰艦互望」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fSVGlOr2oje4Y85Z-nYl5fq64qs=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JG6NBBCUVAE7FGLVYIKBFLBWDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfSVGlOr2oje4Y85Z-nYl5fq64qs%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJG6NBBCUVAE7FGLVYIKBFLBWDU.jpg&h=c1211da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「超級大黃蜂」戰機在列根號甲板上掠過。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n中美在過去的周末同時在南海舉行軍演，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，一架B-52轟炸機亦從美國本土飛行28小時遠赴南海參與演習。尼米茲號戰鬥群指揮官科克少將表示，他們演習期間和中國軍艦互望。<br />\n<br />\n「他們看到我們，我們也看到他們。」<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n美媒報道，美軍南海演習期間，兩艘航母上的F/A-18「超級大黃蜂」戰機攜帶空對地導彈執行模擬攻擊任務，EA-18G「咆哮者」電子戰機負責演練癱瘓敵方通訊。中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨在例行記者會上批評，美方蓄意派重兵在南海舉行大規模軍演，炫耀武力，完全是別有用心，旨在挑撥地區國家關係，推動南海軍事化，破壞該區和平與穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳解放軍撤離中印邊境<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，中印邊境衝突有緩和迹象。中國外長王毅前晚與印度國家安全顧問多瓦爾通電話，雙方達成四點共識，同意避免衝突升級，盡快分隔一線部隊，亦同意通過特別代表會晤機制加強溝通。路透社昨引述印度消息稱，解放軍開始從爭議地區撤離，昨拆除在加勒萬河谷的帳篷及臨時建築物，軍車亦開始駛離多個中印邊境爭議區域。惟兩國人民矛盾難化解，有Twitter用戶上載照片，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n的告示牌。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/《華爾街日報》"},{"pid":"be82e53adce7a2a5db7b7f20f7d960e766c2cf07","tid":2097911,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c7e7521c6cadd233b17be87b162bc596d33d11","tid":2097911,"uid":294182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:23:39.000Z","msg":"美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec25acbe0d661d41f97f3da232759166003b193","tid":2097911,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"原來華真係有戰艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲以為係擺設嚟"},{"pid":"78466f3bfed772bd906408825e0d34c6085af0f4","tid":2097911,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"印度又差美國一個人情"},{"pid":"cbfd4cd1c1fb55caa1667f12532950a7649ec4ee","tid":2097911,"uid":284064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ec25acbe0d661d41f97f3da232759166003b193","tid":2097911,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"原來華真係有戰艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲以為係擺設嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"戰艦依家係咩標準😂"},{"pid":"bbda37927eabb9c0f8c3205f8fbc88933a308fdf","tid":2097911,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyCrmZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyCrmZF.jpg&h=818f9ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遲d有埋戰機互望"}]}